code: @Override public RoutePolicy createRoutePolicy(CamelContext camelContext, String routeId, NamedNode route) {     DurationRoutePolicy policy = null.     if (fromRouteId == null || PatternHelper.matchPattern(routeId, fromRouteId)) {         policy = new DurationRoutePolicy(camelContext, routeId).         policy.setMaxMessages(maxMessages).         policy.setMaxSeconds(maxSeconds).         policy.setAction(action).     }     return policy. }
